data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! This charming 3-bedroom house is a perfect blend of modern convenience and classic charm, making it a great choice for those looking for a cozy and stylish place to call their own.
The three bedrooms in this house are spacious and bright, offering comfortable retreats for everyone in the family. The master suite is a true oasis, featuring a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with smart bathroom fixtures. You can control the lighting, temperature, and even the music in your bathroom with a simple voice command.

Speaking of bathrooms, this house boasts two gorgeously remodeled bathrooms in total, ensuring that everyone has their own personal space. These bathrooms are a perfect blend of modern elegance and functionality, featuring high-end fixtures and stylish tile.

Step outside, and you'll find a fenced-in yard that's perfect for both relaxation and recreation. A charming shed and chicken coop provide endless possibilities for hobbies and storage.

This house isn't just a place to live; it's a lifestyle. Imagine spending your mornings sipping coffee on the front porch, tending to your garden, or collecting fresh eggs from your very own chickens. It's a true sanctuary where you can escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.

Located in a friendly neighborhood with convenient access to schools, parks, and shopping, this home offers the best of both worlds: a serene retreat and easy access to everything you need.

Don't miss your chance to make this house your forever home! Call today for your own private showing!
